  "prompt": "Which is a good inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Washington County AR?",
  "response": "Finding the right inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center can be crucial in the recovery process. In Washington County, AR, you have several options. Here are a few reputable inpatient rehab centers nearby:\n\n1. **Teen Challenge Adventure Ranch** - Located in Morrow, AR, this facility offers a faith-based residential program specifically for male teens who are struggling with addiction.\n\n2. **Decision Point** - Located in Bentonville, AR, Decision Point provides comprehensive inpatient treatment for substance abuse, including medical detoxification and individualized therapy.\n\n3. **Vantage Point Behavioral Health Hospital** - While located in Fayetteville, AR, this facility offers inpatient treatment for various forms of addiction, including specialized programs for dual diagnosis.\n\n4. **Springwoods Behavioral Health** - Situated in Fayetteville, AR, Springwoods offers inpatient treatment services for substance use disorders, alongside a range of mental health programs.\n\nIt's important to visit these centers, talk to the staff, and possibly look at reviews from former patients to find the best fit for your specific needs. Consulting with a healthcare provider can also help you make a more informed decision.",
